$ Excel Object Model: Window.ScrollRow and Window.ScrollColumn

sa:

  → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Application/goto[`application.goto`]

  In order to move a → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Worksheet to its initial position (Cell `A1` in the top left corner),
  → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Range/select[`.cells(1,1).select`] can be used.

  The `.scrollIntoView` and `.scrollWorkbookTabs` methods.

  The → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Window[`window`] object
